item.description: Jillian's Billiard's Club (50 Phillippe Cote St., Manchester, NH) is sponsoring a debate watching party for Ron Paul supporters on Saturday night. It will feature free food, guest speakers, and live entertainment. Goldenstate Band, Jordan Page, Tom Woods, and Adam Kokesh are all scheduled to be in attendance. This would be a great place for us all to meet and have a great time!!
item.name: Debate Watching Party January 7th in N.H.
